ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Saoyú—Æehdacho (Grizzly Bear Mountain and Scented Grass Hills) National Historic Site) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SAOYU - AEEHDACHO (GRIZZLY BEAR MOUNTAIN AND SCENTED GRASS HILLS) NATIONAL HISTORIC SITE) ORDER - which provides for (a) the withdrawal from disposal of some 5,565 square kilometres of land in the Northwest Territories; and (b) the repeal of a similar Withdrawal from Disposal Order made in 2005.
